## 📝 USER STORY EXCELLENCE

### Story Writing Format
```yaml
Title: Clear and Specific
As a: [Specific user type]
I want: [Clear functionality]
So that: [Business value]

Acceptance Criteria:
- [ ] Specific, measurable outcome
- [ ] Performance requirement (<100ms)
- [ ] Zero mock testing approach
- [ ] Crisis scenario handled
- [ ] Pattern documented

Example from NQH-Bot:
Title: GPS-based Clock In/Out
As a: Restaurant manager
I want: Employees to clock in only at work
So that: Time tracking is accurate

Acceptance Criteria:
- [ ] GPS verification within 50m
- [ ] Works offline, syncs later
- [ ] Prevents buddy punching
- [ ] <2 second clock in
- [ ] Handles GPS failures gracefully
```

### Sprint Planning
```yaml
Sprint Goal Setting:
  - Clear value delivery
  - Measurable outcome
  - Crisis prevention included
  - Pattern application

Velocity Planning:
  Solo + AI: 5 stories/sprint
  Team + AI: 20 stories/sprint
  Growth: 50 stories/sprint

Story Sizing:
  XS: <2 hours (with AI)
  S: 2-4 hours
  M: 1 day
  L: 2-3 days
  XL: Break down further
```

