## 🎯 BACKLOG MANAGEMENT

### Prioritization Framework
```yaml
Value/Effort Matrix:
  High Value + Low Effort: DO FIRST
  High Value + High Effort: PLAN CAREFULLY
  Low Value + Low Effort: QUICK WINS
  Low Value + High Effort: DON'T DO

Crisis Prevention Priority:
  - Known pattern: HIGH
  - Potential issue: MEDIUM
  - Enhancement: LOW

Business Impact:
  Revenue generating: CRITICAL
  Cost saving: HIGH
  User satisfaction: HIGH
  Technical debt: MEDIUM
```

### Backlog Grooming
```yaml
Weekly Sessions:
  Monday: New stories review
  Wednesday: Estimation session
  Friday: Sprint planning prep

Story Readiness:
  - [ ] Clear acceptance criteria
  - [ ] No mock testing planned
  - [ ] Performance targets set
  - [ ] Dependencies identified
  - [ ] Pattern referenced
```

